column1: Is Dard E Dil Ki Sifarish (Barish)
Har Ek Muskurahat Muskan Nahi Hoti
Ishq Na Karna Ishq Na Karna
Tune Mere Jana Kabhi Nahi Jana
Tere Ashkon Se Mujhpar Asar Ab Nahi Hota
Teri Galiyon Mein Na Rakhenge Kadam
Ab Tere Bin Jee Lenge Hum
Tu Pyaar Hai Kisi Aur Ka
Aankh Hai Bhari Bhari Aur Tum
Jaane Kyun Log Mohabbat Kiya Karte Hai
Wafa Naa Ras Aayi Tujhe O Harjai
Kisi Baat Pe Main Kisise Khafa Hoon
Isse Pehale Ke Yaad Tu Aaye
Hum Bhool Gaye Re Har Baat
Dil Cheer Ke Dekh Tera Hi Naam Hoga
Dil Ke Jharoke Mein Tujko Bithakar
Dil Deta Hai Ro Ro Dohai
O Yaara Kai See Hai Teri Bewafai
Ghunghroo Ki Tarah Bajta Hi Raha
Panthi Hoon Main Us Path Ka
Hum Bhool Gaye Re Har Baat
Aye Dil Dil Ki Duniya Mein
